<tr>
<td width="83%">
<br />
<font class="post">
Direct Damage spells in Player vs. Player combat can only do up to 75% damage of the target's maximum hit points in a single hit. This modification is done before resists are taken into account. For example, if a player has 1000 hit points when fully healed, no single direct damage spell will do more than 750 damage to him in a single hit. <br /><br /><br /><br />So a spell will never do more than 75% total dmg. 
</font>
<br />
<br />
